# 🎬 Movie Explorer

Welcome to **Movie Explorer** – a sleek and modern React-based web app that helps you discover trending movies and search for your favorites effortlessly.

## 🔍 Features

- 🔥 Browse **Trending Movies** (updated daily)
- 🔎 **Search** any movie by name
- 📊 See **movie ratings** (overall score)
- 📝 View **detailed movie information**:
  - Overview
  - Release date
  - Poster
  - Vote average

## 🛠️ Built With

- React
- Node.js
- Tailwind
- Appwrite
